{"tid":1921742,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"呢度有立法會配票100%成功嘅方法","createTime":"2020-03-12T06:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T09:38:31.000Z","uid":67553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"95dfd375301d6004e11039825e4b0e32ff58dcac","tid":1921742,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:57:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/亂數救港-一個違背民主原則以爭取民主的配票概念/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%BA%82%E6%95%B8%E6%95%91%E6%B8%AF-%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E9%81%95%E8%83%8C%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E5%8E%9F%E5%89%87%E4%BB%A5%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E7%9A%84%E9%85%8D%E7%A5%A8%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%2F&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lbnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=6215f16b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%BA%82%E6%95%B8%E6%95%91%E6%B8%AF-%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E9%81%95%E8%83%8C%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E5%8E%9F%E5%89%87%E4%BB%A5%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E7%9A%84%E9%85%8D%E7%A5%A8%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%2F&h=6a1c8a84\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/亂數救港-一個違背民主原則以爭取民主的配票概念/</a><br />\n<br />\nTLDR:<br />\n你擲一粒骰好多次嘅時候，基本上得出每一個結果嘅次數係一樣。同樣地，用random number 嚟分配自己投邊位侯選人，就可以好準確咁分配每個人嘅得票。<br />\n<br />\n當然喺選舉上，我哋唔會用一粒骰仔嚟實行，因為有太多不確定因素會影響個結果。我哋可以用一個app嚟generate 自己要投邊個。Random 嘅好處就係唔需要上網都可以做到，咁就唔怕被人網絡攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n好似隔離post 咁講，我哋可以用蘋果付費subscriber 嚟分，例如喺3月前已經畀過錢嘅人就可以用呢個功能，咁就可以更加安全地確保有幾多人真係會跟住投票。<br />\n<br />\n當然實際嘅實行要再諗，但係覺得有得諗嘅可以推下呢個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c19b74024aea78afaae979991e6b0755fc6bc4","tid":1921742,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47aa80d0d632a0480b51da7b219f6d4da658396","tid":1921742,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:5